title: Elgar - Enigma Variations, Marches - Previn, RPO
description:
Elgar: "Enigma" Variations, Pomp and Circumstance Marches Nos. 1 - 5.

Sir Edward Elgar's "Enigma" Variations and Pomp and Circumstance Marches Nos. 1 - 5, performed by the Royal Philharmonic Orchestra under Andre Previn, and released by Philips in 1986. Still the best recordings of these pieces that you're likely to hear-in this person's opinion.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
